For machine translation (MT) tasks, all examples should be in the format

<input sentence><tab><output sentence><\n>,

and the data files should be placed in data/wmt14/en_de/ or similarly named folders, depeding on the task definition.
If the data originally comes in separate files for source and target language, run

python prepare_MT_data.py <output file> <src lang file> <trg lang file>

for each of train, dev, and (optionally) test first. Using the example data in this folder, this would be:

python prepare_MT_data.py ../../data/wmt14/en_de/train.tsv example_data/train.en example_data/train.de
python prepare_MT_data.py ../../data/wmt14/en_de/val.tsv example_data/dev.en example_data/dev.de

For a config example, please refer to: ../../jiant/config/wmt14_en_de.conf

Training of an MT model can then be started with

(cd ../../)
python main.py --config_file jiant/config/wmt14_en_de.conf
